      "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">&ldquo;Smudge cells&rdquo; in the peripheral smear are characteristic of:</span></span></span></p>",
